<%- include('../partials/head') %>
<section class="guide-hero-v35">
  <p class="eyebrow">Verification Checklist</p>
  <h1>Buyer checklist for used wall printers.</h1>
  <p>Wall Printer Exchange is not an inspection, escrow, payment, shipping, or warranty provider. Use this checklist before any purchase decision.</p>
</section>

<section class="checklist-grid-v35">
  <article>
    <span>Identity</span>
    <h2>Seller and ownership</h2>
    <ul>
      <li>Confirm seller name, company, email, phone, WhatsApp, and business details where applicable.</li>
      <li>Ask for invoice, purchase record, serial number, nameplate, or other ownership documents.</li>
      <li>Confirm the seller is authorized to sell and that there is no undisclosed lien or ownership dispute.</li>
    </ul>
  </article>
  <article>
    <span>Condition</span>
    <h2>Machine and printheads</h2>
    <ul>
      <li>Request recent photos of the full machine, printheads, rails, ink system, control box, software screen, and accessories.</li>
      <li>Arrange a live video demonstration showing startup, movement, nozzle test, and real printing if possible.</li>
      <li>Check printhead model, number of heads, nozzle condition, ink flow, replacement history, and print quality evidence.</li>
    </ul>
  </article>
  <article>
    <span>Package</span>
    <h2>Accessories and history</h2>
    <ul>
      <li>Confirm rails, extension poles, computer, software, dongle, ink, spare parts, tools, manuals, and packaging materials.</li>
      <li>Ask about production year, purchase year, usage frequency, maintenance, repairs, known defects, and storage condition.</li>
      <li>Clarify whether the machine is currently working, partly working, or requires repair.</li>
    </ul>
  </article>
  <article>
    <span>Deal terms</span>
    <h2>Payment and logistics</h2>
    <ul>
      <li>Clarify packaging, pickup address, dimensions, weight, export documents, customs, duties, taxes, insurance, and shipping damage responsibility.</li>
      <li>Use a written agreement covering condition, included items, price, payment terms, delivery terms, inspection rights, refund terms, and after-sale responsibilities.</li>
      <li>Avoid full payment before verifying seller identity, machine condition, and transaction terms.</li>
    </ul>
  </article>
</section>

<section class="guide-note-v35">
  <h2>Important platform note</h2>
  <p>Wall Printer Exchange does not hold buyer funds and does not guarantee machine condition, ownership, print quality, shipping outcome, customs clearance, installation, training, or after-sales support.</p>
</section>
